    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As a new initiate to <i><strong>The Order</strong></i> meant to safeguard the world from harm, the threats have outnumbered <i><strong>The Order</strong></i> so severely that without proper training, help or oversight you're being thrown to the wolves.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>It's time to grind.</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127110/extras/8b2bb712fe15aad2cc1e1474e73649c7.avif?t=1767882403\" width=616 height=154 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take on stronger and stronger monsters as you prepare yourself to take on stronger and stronger monsters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>NOTE: Idle play is a main component to this game.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Key Features</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A deceptively deep combat system that supports tons of player builds</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No disposable gear here-- collect, tweak, upgrade and hone equipment to your playstyle.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6 zones with varied aesthetics/monsters</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tons of unique effects</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Light town building elements</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tons of challenges and quests to tackle</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Soup!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Number will in fact... go up</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127110/extras/2eef3a913f3351e54216e3d52f42fab0.avif?t=1767882403\" width=616 height=154 /></span></p>",
